useful to baseball researchers

00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:49.200
and data analysis and,
hopefully, can form a model

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:51.930
for other types of collections.

00:02:51.930 --> 00:02:54.500
It's always fun to show what
could be quickly put together

00:02:54.500 --> 00:02:56.340
