00:21:30.970 --> 00:21:34.560
and other Negro League teams
before he ever kissed an angel

00:21:34.560 --> 00:21:36.130
good morning.

00:21:36.130 --> 00:21:39.160
Pride is now part owner
of the Texas Rangers

00:21:39.160 --> 00:21:43.680
and at 84 years old still
trains with them every spring.

00:21:45.550 --> 00:21:49.030
We're able to connect baseball
across various collections

00:21:49.030 --> 00:21:51.400
and subject areas
