including a ring,
magazines, and photographs.

00:26:25.420 --> 00:26:27.320
The collection objects
span different aspects

00:26:27.320 --> 00:26:30.700
of Jackie Robinson's career,
not only as a baseball player,

00:26:30.700 --> 00:26:34.370
but as a family man and activist
who impacted both baseball

00:26:34.370 --> 00:26:36.940
and African American community.

