So what we'll do, just so you
know, is over the coming week

01:04:12.110 --> 01:04:15.040
or two, we'll fix
some of the things

01:04:15.040 --> 01:04:17.240
that you might have seen
-- the alignment issues,

01:04:17.240 --> 01:04:24.120
the bugs that we deftly
