in sort of like how chosen

01:38:22.370 --> 01:38:24.140
of a community it is, right?

01:38:24.140 --> 01:38:25.440
I mean, many of the communities

01:38:25.440 --> 01:38:27.050
that we're part of,
we are born into.

01:38:27.050 --> 01:38:30.910
