family, we choose our history.

01:38:30.910 --> 01:38:35.740
We do, on some level, choose
our team that we root for,

01:38:35.740 --> 01:38:39.340
and yet our commitment to
that, I think for most of us,

01:38:39.340 --> 01:38:43.190
