-- it it okay to say this?

01:38:43.190 --> 01:38:46.600
Like just as deep as [inaudible]
historical communities

01:38:46.600 --> 01:38:47.900
that we're a part of.

01:38:47.900 --> 01:38:49.870
And I think that can be like a
really good learning [inaudible]

01:38:49.870 --> 01:38:52.740
to think about like, boy, what
does community mean if I feel it

01:38:52.740 --> 01:38:56.550
