long before integration,

01:52:22.390 --> 01:52:23.690
you know?

01:52:23.690 --> 01:52:24.990
And so that -- yeah, it touches
on a lot of different things.

01:52:24.990 --> 01:52:26.290
&gt;&gt; Jordan Ellenberg: But I
think the math people get that,

01:52:26.290 --> 01:52:27.590
by the way.

01:52:27.590 --> 01:52:28.890
&gt;&gt; Clinton Yates: Right.

01:52:28.890 --> 01:52:30.190
&gt;&gt; Jordan Ellenberg: If you talk

01:52:30.190 --> 01:52:31.490
to the mathiest [assumed
