date, the fact it was going on,

01:53:51.760 --> 01:53:53.680
not in Brooklyn,
knocking on doors trying

01:53:53.680 --> 01:53:55.370
to get other Communists
to like sign this petition

01:53:55.370 --> 01:53:57.720
to like get Jackie
Robinson up to the Majors.

