01:54:31.060 --> 01:54:34.290
over a lot of other sports, is
that there's a memory element.

01:54:34.290 --> 01:54:38.190
This for me, it's very different
than a lot of other sports.

01:54:38.190 --> 01:54:42.590
I remember -- you know, the way
I remember baseball games is

01:54:42.590 --> 01:54:43.890
by the notation.

01:54:43.890 --> 01:54:48.360
And there's not necessarily an
apples-to-apples comparison fro

01:54:48.360 --> 01:54:50.220
different -- other
sports, you know?

01:54:50.220 --> 01:54:51.770
And that's why I do it is

01:54:51.770 --> 01:54:53.070
