particularly with the expansion

02:07:58.330 --> 02:08:03.580
of different media and
the ability to broadcast,

02:08:03.580 --> 02:08:07.570
the games in the islands and
in Mexico increasing sucked

02:08:07.570 --> 02:08:11.090
into MLB's commercial organ.

02:08:11.090 --> 02:08:13.670
And that's what I
think is deadly.

02:08:13.670 --> 02:08:17.370
I agree with you
